Telkom is promoting its SmartBroadband Wireless LTE packages as part of the company’s “Summer of more connectivity” promotion. The 24-month contract deals offer users anytime data, Night Surfer data – midnight to 07:00 – and a Huawei B525 LTE router, which can connect up to 64 devices. The packages are intended as fixed-LTE solutions, and consumers are advised to check Telkom’s coverage map before ordering. The company added that LTE users can expect maximum download speeds of up to 90Mbps. “Take The Summer of More and make it your own with Telkom SmartBroadband Wireless LTE Deals,” said Telkom. Telkom’s LTE deals are detailed in the table below.